		{
			dependencies: ["1CAAB5A966BC42BD"]
			description: [
				"&aRats&r are very smart creatures, and you can train them to do many of your tasks. Try using one to automate &nwheat farming&r first. "
				""
				"1. Plant the farm"
				"2. Place a &aRat&r in the middle of it."
				"3. Right-click the &aRat&r to open his inventory, then cycle through his commands, finally clicking on \"&5Harvest&r\""
				"4. Use a &9cheese staff&r to assign him a chest to put the harvest into."
				"5. Sit back and let the &aRat&r do all the work."
				""
				"We're going to need more rats!"
			]
