		{
			dependencies: ["77805105BDA7D030"]
			description: [
				"Your &aRats&r can do other tasks on the farm as well. They can breed animals. They can even kill them for harvesting."
				""
				"Which is great, because you're going to need to harvest a lot of animals in order to make the vitally important &9meatwad&r."
				""
				"Make a &9Mob Filter&r, and then select the animal you want your &aRat&r to hunt. Make sure you don't confuse whitelists and blacklists (they will not target babies either way). Then apply that upgrade to the chosen &aRat&r's interface, and command it to &5Hunt Mobs&r. Sit back and let nature take its course."
				""
				"Don't forget to use your &9Cheese Staff&r to direct all drops to a chest."
			]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
				id: "alexscavesdelight:pure_darkness_knife"
				tag: {
					Damage: 0
				}
			}
