		{
			dependencies: ["12A799586D7DDE9E"]
			description: [
				"Bird meat will be an essential ingredient in this &9meatwad&r. Your world is full of birds of all kinds, in addition to our old favorite, the &aChicken&r. You already made a bird farm in the previous chapter, and it's probably already generating meat on the side. "
				""
				"All you need to do now is direct your &9Rats&r to move that meat into this pipeline."
			]
