		{
			dependencies: ["12A799586D7DDE9E"]
			description: [
				"You will need fish meat to complete this &9meatwad&r. There are a few ways you could go about this."
				""
				"First, you could keep using your &aRats&r. They can be taught to fish using &9Rat Upgrade: Fisherman&r and the &5Harvest&r command."
				""
				"Alternately, you could find some &eShoebills&r. They will also spend their time fishing and dropping plenty of goods for you, and if you feed them &9crocodile eggs&r you can even increase their lure."
				""
				"Choose a path, or maybe do both at the same time."
