		{
			dependencies: ["12A799586D7DDE9E"]
			description: [
				"As with the &9furball&r, you will need to construct your &9meatwad&r from multiple classes of animals."
				""
				"Mammal meat will be a critical component. There are many animals you can farm in order to harvest this, including &aKangaroos&r, &aCows&r, &aSheep&r, &aPigs&r, &aRabbits&r, or even &aBears&r. Pick your favorite and teach your &aRats&r how to harvest them sustainably."
